```plantuml
@startuml UBC-CIC_Student-Connect-App
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "Frontend (PWA)" as Frontend {
  rectangle "ReactJS" as React
}

rectangle "AWS Services" as AWS #lightblue {
  rectangle "AWS Cognito" as Cognito #lightyellow
  rectangle "DynamoDB" as DynamoDB #lightgrey
  rectangle "Elasticsearch" as Elasticsearch #lightcoral
  rectangle "S3 Data Lake" as S3 #aliceblue
  rectangle "Lambda Functions" as Lambda #lightgreen
}

rectangle "Admin Console" as AdminConsole #lightsteelblue {
  rectangle "Kibana" as Kibana
}

' ========== Connections ==========
User --> React : Interact with PWA
React --> Cognito : User Authentication
React --> DynamoDB : Fetch/Store User Preferences
React --> Elasticsearch : Perform Search Queries
React --> Lambda : Trigger Backend Processes
Lambda --> DynamoDB : Fetch and Update Data
Lambda --> Elasticsearch : Update Indices
Lambda --> S3 : Store Data for Archival
DynamoDB --> Elasticsearch : Sync Data via Streams
DynamoDB --> Lambda : Trigger on Data Change
Kibana --> Elasticsearch : Data Visualization and Management
@enduml
```